Fast dispatch. Full transparency.			<h2>World known <br />brands for medical <br />business</h2>					<h2>Radiology equipment and consumables</h2>		One of our main fields of working is radiology equipment and consumables. We provide our products to partners all around the globe. Our partners are official distrib...					
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M19 12L5 12M19 12L13 6M19 12L13 18" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>			
				44 products			<h2>Lab equipment and consumables</h2>		<p>Laboratories requires a vareity of equipment and instrumentation to run tests and research. These staple, workhouse general lab equipment can be found acro...</p>122 products					
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M19 12L5 12M19 12L13 6M19 12L13 18" stroke="#32333B" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>			
							<h2>MRI systems</h2>		MRI systems support precise diagnostic work by delivering detailed imaging of internal organs and soft tissues. Clinics rely on these systems for consistent quality, reliability, and confident medical decisions25 products					
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M19 12L5 12M19 12L13 6M19 12L13 18" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>			
							<h2>Nephrology</h2>		<p>Clinics and hospitals require reliable dialysis equipment and consumables to support kidney treatment. Our nephrology selection includes dialyzers and dry bicarbonate mixes from trusted...</p>7 products					
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M19 12L5 12M19 12L13 6M19 12L13 18" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>			
				<p>Medem LTD, established in Sofia, Bulgaria in 2015, specializes in the buying and selling of quality used medical, imaging, and hospital equipment. Our primary goal is to provide exceptional customer service by meeting the unique needs of our clients in the medical equipment industry.</p>					
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none"><rect width="40" height="40" rx="12" fill="#F1F1F2"></rect><g clip-path="url(#clip0_71_7462)"><path d="M13.0005 15.7C13.0005 15.1165 13.2322 14.5569 13.6448 14.1443C14.0574 13.7318 14.617 13.5 15.2005 13.5H16.2005C16.7814 13.4996 17.3386 13.2696 17.7505 12.86L18.4505 12.16C18.6549 11.9544 18.898 11.7912 19.1657 11.6799C19.4334 11.5685 19.7205 11.5112 20.0105 11.5112C20.3004 11.5112 20.5875 11.5685 20.8552 11.6799C21.1229 11.7912 21.366 11.9544 21.5705 12.16L22.2705 12.86C22.6825 13.27 23.2405 13.5 23.8205 13.5H24.8205C25.4039 13.5 25.9635 13.7318 26.3761 14.1443C26.7887 14.5569 27.0205 15.1165 27.0205 15.7V16.7C27.0205 17.28 27.2505 17.838 27.6605 18.25L28.3605 18.95C28.5661 19.1544 28.7292 19.3975 28.8406 19.6652C28.9519 19.9329 29.0092 20.22 29.0092 20.51C29.0092 20.7999 28.9519 21.087 28.8406 21.3547C28.7292 21.6225 28.5661 21.8655 28.3605 22.07L27.6605 22.77C27.2509 23.1819 27.0208 23.7391 27.0205 24.32V25.32C27.0205 25.9034 26.7887 26.463 26.3761 26.8756C25.9635 27.2882 25.4039 27.52 24.8205 27.52H23.8205C23.2396 27.5203 22.6824 27.7504 22.2705 28.16L21.5705 28.86C21.366 29.0656 21.1229 29.2287 20.8552 29.3401C20.5875 29.4514 20.3004 29.5087 20.0105 29.5087C19.7205 29.5087 19.4334 29.4514 19.1657 29.3401C18.898 29.2287 18.6549 29.0656 18.4505 28.86L17.7505 28.16C17.3386 27.7504 16.7814 27.5203 16.2005 27.52H15.2005C14.617 27.52 14.0574 27.2882 13.6448 26.8756C13.2322 26.463 13.0005 25.9034 13.0005 25.32V24.32C13.0001 23.7391 12.7701 23.1819 12.3605 22.77L11.6605 22.07C11.4549 21.8655 11.2917 21.6225 11.1804 21.3547C11.069 21.087 11.0117 20.7999 11.0117 20.51C11.0117 20.22 11.069 19.9329 11.1804 19.6652C11.2917 19.3975 11.4549 19.1544 11.6605 18.95L12.3605 18.25C12.7701 17.8381 13.0001 17.2809 13.0005 16.7V15.7Z" stroke="#32333B" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M17 20.5L19 22.5L23 18.5" stroke="#32333B" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></g><defs><clipPath id="clip0_71_7462"><rect width="24" height="24" fill="white" transform="translate(8 8.5)"></rect></clipPath></defs></svg>			
							<h2>1000+ certified products</h2>		Ready for immediate shipment — via your transport agent or ours.					
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none"><rect width="40" height="40" rx="12" fill="#F1F1F2"></rect><g clip-path="url(#clip0_71_7480)"><path d="M20.9225 18.2686L27.4539 24.8312C28.182 25.5567 28.182 26.7315 27.4539 27.4561C27.1042 27.804 26.6309 27.9993 26.1376 27.9993C25.6442 27.9993 25.171 27.804 24.8212 27.4561L18.2685 20.9227M20.9225 18.2686L17.3837 14.7297M20.9225 18.2686L21.3648 18.711L23.3934 16.6824C23.5592 16.5165 23.6524 16.2916 23.6524 16.057C23.6524 15.8224 23.5592 15.5974 23.3934 15.4315L20.221 12.259C20.0551 12.0932 19.8301 12 19.5955 12C19.3609 12 19.136 12.0932 18.9701 12.259L16.9415 14.2876L17.3837 14.7297M20.9225 18.2686L18.2685 20.9227M18.2685 20.9227L14.7297 17.3838M18.2685 20.9227L18.7109 21.3651L16.6823 23.3937C16.5164 23.5595 16.2915 23.6527 16.0569 23.6527C15.8223 23.6527 15.5973 23.5595 15.4314 23.3937L12.259 20.2212C12.0932 20.0553 12 19.8303 12 19.5957C12 19.3611 12.0932 19.1361 12.259 18.9702L14.2875 16.9417L14.7297 17.3838M14.7297 17.3838L17.3837 14.7297M12.0757 28H18.2683" stroke="#32333B" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></g><defs><clipPath id="clip0_71_7480"><rect width="24" height="24" fill="white" transform="translate(8 8)"></rect></clipPath></defs></svg>			
							<h2>Transparent deals</h2>		No hidden fees or legal risks. Protected by EU law.					
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none"><rect width="40" height="40" rx="12" fill="#F1F1F2"></rect><g clip-path="url(#clip0_71_7471)"><path d="M12 20.4641C12.3059 22.8493 13.7704 24.9679 15.7647 26.1162M27.0588 18.58C26.8286 16.9222 26.0603 15.3862 24.8721 14.2086C23.6839 13.0309 22.1418 12.2769 20.4834 12.0627C18.8249 11.8486 17.1421 12.1861 15.6942 13.0233C14.2462 13.8605 13.1135 15.151 12.4704 16.6959M12 12.9277V16.6958H15.7647M19.5293 22.348H21.4117C21.6613 22.348 21.9007 22.4472 22.0772 22.6239C22.2537 22.8005 22.3529 23.0401 22.3529 23.29V24.232C22.3529 24.4818 22.2537 24.7214 22.0772 24.8981C21.9007 25.0747 21.6613 25.174 21.4117 25.174H20.4705C20.2209 25.174 19.9815 25.2732 19.805 25.4499C19.6285 25.6266 19.5293 25.8662 19.5293 26.116V27.058C19.5293 27.3078 19.6285 27.5474 19.805 27.7241C19.9815 27.9008 20.2209 28 20.4705 28H22.3529M25.1764 22.348V24.232C25.1764 24.4818 25.2756 24.7214 25.4521 24.8981C25.6286 25.0747 25.868 25.174 26.1176 25.174H27.0588M28 22.348V28" stroke="#32333B" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></g><defs><clipPath id="clip0_71_7471"><rect width="24" height="24" fill="white" transform="translate(8 8)"></rect></clipPath></defs></svg>			
							<h2>Offer within 24 hours</h2>		Get a fast, customized quote designed for your business.					
