							<h2>Globally recognized brands</h2>		Direct supply with zero risk of counterfeit products.			<h2>Why our price is better?</h2>		We maximize your savings by consolidating bulk orders and negotiating the best terms with top suppliers using quantity as our leverage. MEDEM ltd supplies world-leading brands Fujifilm, Agfa, Carestream, Konica Minolta, Sony and more.					
